description: next-intl conventions for locales, messages, and localized routes
globs: "{messages,i18n,app}/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

# i18n

- Never hardcode user-facing strings in components or pages
- Add every new string to **both** `messages/en.json` and `messages/ru.json`
- Use next-intl APIs (`useTranslations`, `getTranslations`) — match patterns in existing pages
- Locale routing lives under `app/[locale]/`; config in `i18n/`
- Error messages shown to users must use i18n keys, not raw server errors
